{"word":"G4291 - προΐστημι - proḯstēmi - pro-is'-tay-mee - Maintain","slug":"G4291","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προΐστημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>proḯstēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pro-is'-tay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Maintain"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x0344;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - proiste&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>pro-is'-tay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2476\">G2476</a>; to <i>stand before</i>, that is, (in rank) to <i>preside</i>, or (by implication) to <i>practise:</i> - maintain, be over, rule."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G547\">G547</a>"}]}